*& Form MAIL_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM MAIL_DATA .
  LOOP AT LT_FINAL INTO LS_FINAL.
    IF LS_FINAL-PROFILE = 'SAP_ALL' OR LS_FINAL-PROFILE = 'SAP_NEW'.
      APPEND LS_FINAL TO LT_MAIL.
    ENDIF.
  ENDLOOP.
ENDFORM.
